    </node>
    <node id="INVOICE">
      <data key="d0">CONCEPT</data>
      <data key="d1">Subscription billing records functioning as the primary table for revenue analysis and customer payment history tracking, containing details like total amounts and service periods.}
Subscription billing records used for revenue analysis and tracking customer payment history. It includes details like invoice number, date, plan, and payment method.}</data>
