    <node id="CONTENT">
      <data key="d0">CONCEPT</data>
      <data key="d1">Movies, TV shows, or media available for streaming, linked to viewing events and analyzed for performance metrics like popularity and engagement.}
Video content catalog with details about available media, including title, genre, duration, and licensing costs.}Video content catalog containing metadata about available media titles. Includes identifiers, titles, genres, durations, and licensing costs.}</data>
