    <node id="CUSTOMER_ID">
      <data key="d0">ATTRIBUTE</data>
      <data key="d1">Unique identifier for customers, used across entities (streams, invoice, customer) to establish relationships and enable joins for unified analysis.}
Foreign key in the invoice table linking to the customer entity, enabling association between billing records and subscribers.}Foreign key in invoice table linking to customer entity. Also serves as primary key in customer table.}Unique identifier for each subscriber, serving as the primary key for the customer entity.}</data>
